{"tid":762473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮顧問： 國際貿易破壞　中國造成","createTime":"2018-07-31T10:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T01:37:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b864e9f5e2517258dc4160eeadd6ce73c8510b2e","tid":762473,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180731/20464825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180731%2F20464825&d=PHC3uQZ8Qvt1qIW%2FsaJPA7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=59b4338b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180731%2F20464825&h=45cbe07a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180731/20464825</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月31日 <br />\n<br />\n白宮顧問：<br />\n國際貿易破壞　中國造成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180731/large/a1405a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180731%2Flarge%2Fa1405a.gif&h=a8e5c9c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■隨歐盟與美國展開貿易談判，庫德洛形容中國正被孤立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國與歐盟達成貿易協議後，美國白宮經濟顧問庫德洛（Larry Kudlow）周日接連炮轟中國，狠批中國不按規則辦事，國際貿易體系受到破壞，大部份是中國造成的；認為美歐達成貿易共識，有助孤立中國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n狠批中國不按規則辦事<br />\n<br />\n庫德洛周日接受美國有線電視新聞網絡訪問時，為美國總統特朗普對華貿易政策作出辯護，狠批中國不按規則辦事，國際貿易體系受到破壞，大部份是中國造成的。他接受美國哥倫比亞電視台專訪時表示，中美爆發貿易戰之際，美歐上周四達成貿易協議，有助達致孤立中國的目的。他指，隨着美歐達成貿易協議，美國墨西哥貿易協定預期日內達成，中方面臨的壓力上升，有利達成中美貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n這是庫德洛三日內三度談及中美貿易戰。特朗普上周四在白宮與歐盟主席容克（Jean-Claude Juncker）會談，雙方同意消除貿易壁壘致力零關稅，庫德洛同日接受美國霍士電視訪問時表示，容克近日和特朗普會面時承諾，歐盟將在貿易問題上和美聯手對抗中國。<br />\n<br />\n庫德洛引容克透露，中國在貿易問題上曾拉攏歐盟，但被歐盟拒絕。庫德洛嚴厲批評中國透過關稅不公平貿易，以及竊取知識產權等行為，破壞了全球的貿易體系，美國有必要撥亂反正。<br />\n<br />\nCNN/CBS  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n王毅見英外相：別干涉港內部事務<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n內憂外患 習出席北戴河會議難輕鬆"},{"pid":"c9d826a4bb613ae4c7288ee1e23c6a5e9549447a","tid":762473,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T11:18:22.000Z","msg":"支那國雜總：堅決抵制貿易保護主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134bc7d0ed29476e2dea66513e05ace04a0242fe","tid":762473,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T11:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亮劍"},{"pid":"5759f15445781fa7ed24de5582536e799aa0fd89","tid":762473,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T11:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68495d1f723aa6e54b2aefad86a45085daacde4","tid":762473,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T01:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77eac1d872e118ea92bc56787c726c835f572de3","tid":762473,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T01:37:34.000Z","msg":"按規則做事，能搵大錢嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}